the world. It is a way I have of driving off the spleen and regulating          gur jbeyq. Vg vf n jnl V unir bs qevivat bss gur fcyrra naq erthyngvat
the circulation. Whenever I find myself growing grim about the mouth;           gur pvephyngvba. Jurarire V svaq zlfrys tebjvat tevz nobhg gur zbhgu;
