mine own. Yet this is nothing: I leave eternity to Thee; for what is man        zvar bja. Lrg guvf vf abguvat: V yrnir rgreavgl gb Gurr; sbe jung vf zna
that he should live out the lifetime of his God?"                               gung ur fubhyq yvir bhg gur yvsrgvzr bs uvf Tbq?"
                                                                                
He said no more, but slowly waving a benediction, covered his face with         Ur fnvq ab zber, ohg fybjyl jnivat n orarqvpgvba, pbirerq uvf snpr jvgu
his hands, and so remained kneeling, till all the people had departed,          uvf unaqf, naq fb erznvarq xarryvat, gvyy nyy gur crbcyr unq qrcnegrq,
and he was left alone in the place.                                             naq ur jnf yrsg nybar va gur cynpr.
                                                                                
                                                                                
                                                                                
