Queequeg was a native of Rokovoko, an island far away to the West and           Dhrrdhrt jnf n angvir bs Ebxbibxb, na vfynaq sne njnl gb gur Jrfg naq
South. It is not down in any map; true places never are.                        Fbhgu. Vg vf abg qbja va nal znc; gehr cynprf arire ner.
                                                                                
When a new-hatched savage running wild about his native woodlands in            Jura n arj-ungpurq fnintr ehaavat jvyq nobhg uvf angvir jbbqynaqf va
