CHAPTER 23. The Lee Shore.                                                      PUNCGRE 23. Gur Yrr Fuber.
                                                                                
                                                                                
Some chapters back, one Bulkington was spoken of, a tall, newlanded             Fbzr puncgref onpx, bar Ohyxvatgba jnf fcbxra bs, n gnyy, arjynaqrq
