But as in landlessness alone resides highest truth, shoreless,                  Ohg nf va ynaqyrffarff nybar erfvqrf uvturfg gehgu, fuberyrff,
indefinite as God--so, better is it to perish in that howling infinite,         vaqrsvavgr nf Tbq--fb, orggre vf vg gb crevfu va gung ubjyvat vasvavgr,
