ocean-perishing--straight up, leaps thy apotheosis!                             bprna-crevfuvat--fgenvtug hc, yrncf gul ncbgurbfvf!
                                                                                
                                                                                
                                                                                
CHAPTER 24. The Advocate.                                                       PUNCGRE 24. Gur Nqibpngr.
                                                                                
                                                                                
As Queequeg and I are now fairly embarked in this business of whaling;          Nf Dhrrdhrt naq V ner abj snveyl rzonexrq va guvf ohfvarff bs junyvat;
and as this business of whaling has somehow come to be regarded among           naq nf guvf ohfvarff bs junyvat unf fbzrubj pbzr gb or ertneqrq nzbat
landsmen as a rather unpoetical and disreputable pursuit; therefore, I          ynaqfzra nf n engure hacbrgvpny naq qvferchgnoyr chefhvg; gurersber, V
