to us hunters of whales.                                                        gb hf uhagref bs junyrf.
                                                                                
In the first place, it may be deemed almost superfluous to establish            Va gur svefg cynpr, vg znl or qrrzrq nyzbfg fhcresyhbhf gb rfgnoyvfu
the fact, that among people at large, the business of whaling is not            gur snpg, gung nzbat crbcyr ng ynetr, gur ohfvarff bs junyvat vf abg
accounted on a level with what are called the liberal professions. If a         nppbhagrq ba n yriry jvgu jung ner pnyyrq gur yvoreny cebsrffvbaf. Vs n
stranger were introduced into any miscellaneous metropolitan society,           fgenatre jrer vagebqhprq vagb nal zvfpryynarbhf zrgebcbyvgna fbpvrgl,
it would but slightly advance the general opinion of his merits, were           vg jbhyq ohg fyvtugyl nqinapr gur trareny bcvavba bs uvf zrevgf, jrer
he presented to the company as a harpooneer, say; and if in emulation           ur cerfragrq gb gur pbzcnal nf n unecbbarre, fnl; naq vs va rzhyngvba
of the naval officers he should append the initials S.W.F. (Sperm               bs gur aniny bssvpref ur fubhyq nccraq gur vavgvnyf F.J.S. (Fcrez
Whale Fishery) to his visiting card, such a procedure would be deemed           Junyr Svfurel) gb uvf ivfvgvat pneq, fhpu n cebprqher jbhyq or qrrzrq
pre-eminently presuming and ridiculous.                                         cer-rzvaragyl cerfhzvat naq evqvphybhf.
                                                                                
Doubtless one leading reason why the world declines honouring us                Qbhogyrff bar yrnqvat ernfba jul gur jbeyq qrpyvarf ubabhevat hf
whalemen, is this: they think that, at best, our vocation amounts to a          junyrzra, vf guvf: gurl guvax gung, ng orfg, bhe ibpngvba nzbhagf gb n
butchering sort of business; and that when actively engaged therein, we         ohgpurevat fbeg bs ohfvarff; naq gung jura npgviryl ratntrq gurerva, jr
are surrounded by all manner of defilements. Butchers we are, that is           ner fheebhaqrq ol nyy znaare bs qrsvyrzragf. Ohgpuref jr ner, gung vf
true. But butchers, also, and butchers of the bloodiest badge have been         gehr. Ohg ohgpuref, nyfb, naq ohgpuref bs gur oybbqvrfg onqtr unir orra
all Martial Commanders whom the world invariably delights to honour. And        nyy Znegvny Pbzznaqref jubz gur jbeyq vainevnoyl qryvtugf gb ubabhe. Naq
as for the matter of the alleged uncleanliness of our business, ye shall        nf sbe gur znggre bs gur nyyrtrq hapyrnayvarff bs bhe ohfvarff, lr funyy
soon be initiated into certain facts hitherto pretty generally unknown,         fbba or vavgvngrq vagb pregnva snpgf uvguregb cerggl trarenyyl haxabja,
and which, upon the whole, will triumphantly plant the sperm whale-ship         naq juvpu, hcba gur jubyr, jvyy gevhzcunagyl cynag gur fcrez junyr-fuvc
at least among the cleanliest things of this tidy earth. But even               ng yrnfg nzbat gur pyrnayvrfg guvatf bs guvf gvql rnegu. Ohg rira
granting the charge in question to be true; what disordered slippery            tenagvat gur punetr va dhrfgvba gb or gehr; jung qvfbeqrerq fyvccrel
decks of a whale-ship are comparable to the unspeakable carrion of those        qrpxf bs n junyr-fuvc ner pbzcnenoyr gb gur hafcrnxnoyr pneevba bs gubfr
battle-fields from which so many soldiers return to drink in all ladies'        onggyr-svryqf sebz juvpu fb znal fbyqvref erghea gb qevax va nyy ynqvrf'
plaudits? And if the idea of peril so much enhances the popular conceit         cynhqvgf? Naq vs gur vqrn bs crevy fb zhpu raunaprf gur cbchyne pbaprvg
of the soldier's profession; let me assure ye that many a veteran               bs gur fbyqvre'f cebsrffvba; yrg zr nffher lr gung znal n irgrena
who has freely marched up to a battery, would quickly recoil at the             jub unf serryl znepurq hc gb n onggrel, jbhyq dhvpxyl erpbvy ng gur
