over his head. For what are the comprehensible terrors of man compared          bire uvf urnq. Sbe jung ner gur pbzcerurafvoyr greebef bs zna pbzcnerq
with the interlinked terrors and wonders of God!                                jvgu gur vagreyvaxrq greebef naq jbaqref bs Tbq!
                                                                                
But, though the world scouts at us whale hunters, yet does it                   Ohg, gubhtu gur jbeyq fpbhgf ng hf junyr uhagref, lrg qbrf vg
