But this is not the half; look again.                                           Ohg guvf vf abg gur unys; ybbx ntnva.
                                                                                
I freely assert, that the cosmopolite philosopher cannot, for his life,         V serryl nffreg, gung gur pbfzbcbyvgr cuvybfbcure pnaabg, sbe uvf yvsr,
point out one single peaceful influence, which within the last sixty            cbvag bhg bar fvatyr crnprshy vasyhrapr, juvpu jvguva gur ynfg fvkgl
