pregnant from her womb. It would be a hopeless, endless task to                 certanag sebz ure jbzo. Vg jbhyq or n ubcryrff, raqyrff gnfx gb
catalogue all these things. Let a handful suffice. For many years past          pngnybthr nyy gurfr guvatf. Yrg n unaqshy fhssvpr. Sbe znal lrnef cnfg
the whale-ship has been the pioneer in ferreting out the remotest and           gur junyr-fuvc unf orra gur cvbarre va sreergvat bhg gur erzbgrfg naq
least known parts of the earth. She has explored seas and archipelagoes         yrnfg xabja cnegf bs gur rnegu. Fur unf rkcyberq frnf naq nepuvcryntbrf
which had no chart, where no Cook or Vancouver had ever sailed. If              juvpu unq ab puneg, jurer ab Pbbx be Inapbhire unq rire fnvyrq. Vs
American and European men-of-war now peacefully ride in once savage             Nzrevpna naq Rhebcrna zra-bs-jne abj crnprshyyl evqr va bapr fnintr
harbors, let them fire salutes to the honour and glory of the                   uneobef, yrg gurz sver fnyhgrf gb gur ubabhe naq tybel bs gur
whale-ship, which originally showed them the way, and first interpreted         junyr-fuvc, juvpu bevtvanyyl fubjrq gurz gur jnl, naq svefg vagrecergrq
