readiness anew. For, when Stubb dressed, instead of first putting his           ernqvarff narj. Sbe, jura Fghoo qerffrq, vafgrnq bs svefg chggvat uvf
legs into his trowsers, he put his pipe into his mouth.                         yrtf vagb uvf gebjfref, ur chg uvf cvcr vagb uvf zbhgu.
                                                                                
I say this continual smoking must have been one cause, at least, of his         V fnl guvf pbagvahny fzbxvat zhfg unir orra bar pnhfr, ng yrnfg, bs uvf
