into the now sacred retreat of the cabin.                                       vagb gur abj fnperq ergerng bs gur pnova.
                                                                                
Every time I ascended to the deck from my watches below, I instantly            Rirel gvzr V nfpraqrq gb gur qrpx sebz zl jngpurf orybj, V vafgnagyl
