Though the long period of a Southern whaling voyage (by far the longest         Gubhtu gur ybat crevbq bs n Fbhgurea junyvat iblntr (ol sne gur ybatrfg
of all voyages now or ever made by man), the peculiar perils of it, and         bs nyy iblntrf abj be rire znqr ol zna), gur crphyvne crevyf bs vg, naq
