CHAPTER 41. Moby Dick.                                                          PUNCGRE 41. Zbol Qvpx.
                                                                                
                                                                                
I, Ishmael, was one of that crew; my shouts had gone up with the rest;          V, Vfuznry, jnf bar bs gung perj; zl fubhgf unq tbar hc jvgu gur erfg;
my oath had been welded with theirs; and stronger I shouted, and more           zl bngu unq orra jryqrq jvgu gurvef; naq fgebatre V fubhgrq, naq zber
did I hammer and clinch my oath, because of the dread in my soul. A             qvq V unzzre naq pyvapu zl bngu, orpnhfr bs gur qernq va zl fbhy. N
wild, mystical, sympathetical feeling was in me; Ahab's quenchless feud         jvyq, zlfgvpny, flzcngurgvpny srryvat jnf va zr; Nuno'f dhrapuyrff srhq
seemed mine. With greedy ears I learned the history of that murderous           frrzrq zvar. Jvgu terrql rnef V yrnearq gur uvfgbel bs gung zheqrebhf
monster against whom I and all the others had taken our oaths of                zbafgre ntnvafg jubz V naq nyy gur bguref unq gnxra bhe bnguf bs
violence and revenge.                                                           ivbyrapr naq eriratr.
                                                                                
For some time past, though at intervals only, the unaccompanied,                Sbe fbzr gvzr cnfg, gubhtu ng vagreinyf bayl, gur hanppbzcnavrq,
secluded White Whale had haunted those uncivilized seas mostly                  frpyhqrq Juvgr Junyr unq unhagrq gubfr hapvivyvmrq frnf zbfgyl
frequented by the Sperm Whale fishermen. But not all of them knew of his        serdhragrq ol gur Fcrez Junyr svfurezra. Ohg abg nyy bs gurz xarj bs uvf
existence; only a few of them, comparatively, had knowingly seen him;           rkvfgrapr; bayl n srj bs gurz, pbzcnengviryl, unq xabjvatyl frra uvz;
while the number who as yet had actually and knowingly given battle to          juvyr gur ahzore jub nf lrg unq npghnyyl naq xabjvatyl tvira onggyr gb
him, was small indeed. For, owing to the large number of whale-cruisers;        uvz, jnf fznyy vaqrrq. Sbe, bjvat gb gur ynetr ahzore bs junyr-pehvfref;
the disorderly way they were sprinkled over the entire watery                   gur qvfbeqreyl jnl gurl jrer fcevaxyrq bire gur ragver jngrel
circumference, many of them adventurously pushing their quest along             pvephzsrerapr, znal bs gurz nqiraghebhfyl chfuvat gurve dhrfg nybat
solitary latitudes, so as seldom or never for a whole twelvemonth or            fbyvgnel yngvghqrf, fb nf fryqbz be arire sbe n jubyr gjryirzbagu be
more on a stretch, to encounter a single news-telling sail of any sort;         zber ba n fgergpu, gb rapbhagre n fvatyr arjf-gryyvat fnvy bs nal fbeg;
the inordinate length of each separate voyage; the irregularity of the          gur vabeqvangr yratgu bs rnpu frcnengr iblntr; gur veerthynevgl bs gur
times of sailing from home; all these, with other circumstances, direct         gvzrf bs fnvyvat sebz ubzr; nyy gurfr, jvgu bgure pvephzfgnaprf, qverpg
and indirect, long obstructed the spread through the whole world-wide           naq vaqverpg, ybat bofgehpgrq gur fcernq guebhtu gur jubyr jbeyq-jvqr
whaling-fleet of the special individualizing tidings concerning Moby            junyvat-syrrg bs gur fcrpvny vaqvivqhnyvmvat gvqvatf pbapreavat Zbol
Dick. It was hardly to be doubted, that several vessels reported to have        Qvpx. Vg jnf uneqyl gb or qbhogrq, gung frireny irffryf ercbegrq gb unir
encountered, at such or such a time, or on such or such a meridian,             rapbhagrerq, ng fhpu be fhpu n gvzr, be ba fhpu be fhpu n zrevqvna,
a Sperm Whale of uncommon magnitude and malignity, which whale, after           n Fcrez Junyr bs hapbzzba zntavghqr naq znyvtavgl, juvpu junyr, nsgre
doing great mischief to his assailants, had completely escaped them; to         qbvat terng zvfpuvrs gb uvf nffnvynagf, unq pbzcyrgryl rfpncrq gurz; gb
some minds it was not an unfair presumption, I say, that the whale in           fbzr zvaqf vg jnf abg na hasnve cerfhzcgvba, V fnl, gung gur junyr va
question must have been no other than Moby Dick. Yet as of late the             dhrfgvba zhfg unir orra ab bgure guna Zbol Qvpx. Lrg nf bs yngr gur
Sperm Whale fishery had been marked by various and not unfrequent               Fcrez Junyr svfurel unq orra znexrq ol inevbhf naq abg haserdhrag
