Nor did wild rumors of all sorts fail to exaggerate, and still the more         Abe qvq jvyq ehzbef bs nyy fbegf snvy gb rknttrengr, naq fgvyy gur zber
horrify the true histories of these deadly encounters. For not only do          ubeevsl gur gehr uvfgbevrf bs gurfr qrnqyl rapbhagref. Sbe abg bayl qb
fabulous rumors naturally grow out of the very body of all surprising           snohybhf ehzbef anghenyyl tebj bhg bs gur irel obql bs nyy fhecevfvat
terrible events,--as the smitten tree gives birth to its fungi; but, in         greevoyr riragf,--nf gur fzvggra gerr tvirf ovegu gb vgf shatv; ohg, va
maritime life, far more than in that of terra firma, wild rumors abound,        znevgvzr yvsr, sne zber guna va gung bs green svezn, jvyq ehzbef nobhaq,
wherever there is any adequate reality for them to cling to. And as the         jurerire gurer vf nal nqrdhngr ernyvgl sbe gurz gb pyvat gb. Naq nf gur
sea surpasses the land in this matter, so the whale fishery surpasses           frn fhecnffrf gur ynaq va guvf znggre, fb gur junyr svfurel fhecnffrf
every other sort of maritime life, in the wonderfulness and fearfulness         rirel bgure fbeg bs znevgvzr yvsr, va gur jbaqreshyarff naq srneshyarff
of the rumors which sometimes circulate there. For not only are whalemen        bs gur ehzbef juvpu fbzrgvzrf pvephyngr gurer. Sbe abg bayl ner junyrzra
as a body unexempt from that ignorance and superstitiousness hereditary         nf n obql harkrzcg sebz gung vtabenapr naq fhcrefgvgvbhfarff urerqvgnel
to all sailors; but of all sailors, they are by all odds the most               gb nyy fnvybef; ohg bs nyy fnvybef, gurl ner ol nyy bqqf gur zbfg
directly brought into contact with whatever is appallingly astonishing          qverpgyl oebhtug vagb pbagnpg jvgu jungrire vf nccnyyvatyl nfgbavfuvat
in the sea; face to face they not only eye its greatest marvels, but,           va gur frn; snpr gb snpr gurl abg bayl rlr vgf terngrfg zneiryf, ohg,
hand to jaw, give battle to them. Alone, in such remotest waters, that          unaq gb wnj, tvir onggyr gb gurz. Nybar, va fhpu erzbgrfg jngref, gung
though you sailed a thousand miles, and passed a thousand shores, you           gubhtu lbh fnvyrq n gubhfnaq zvyrf, naq cnffrq n gubhfnaq fuberf, lbh
would not come to any chiseled hearth-stone, or aught hospitable beneath        jbhyq abg pbzr gb nal puvfryrq urnegu-fgbar, be nhtug ubfcvgnoyr orarngu
that part of the sun; in such latitudes and longitudes, pursuing too            gung cneg bs gur fha; va fhpu yngvghqrf naq ybatvghqrf, chefhvat gbb
such a calling as he does, the whaleman is wrapped by influences all            fhpu n pnyyvat nf ur qbrf, gur junyrzna vf jenccrq ol vasyhraprf nyy
tending to make his fancy pregnant with many a mighty birth.                    graqvat gb znxr uvf snapl certanag jvgu znal n zvtugl ovegu.
                                                                                
No wonder, then, that ever gathering volume from the mere transit over          Ab jbaqre, gura, gung rire tngurevat ibyhzr sebz gur zrer genafvg bire
