CHAPTER 42. The Whiteness of The Whale.                                         PUNCGRE 42. Gur Juvgrarff bs Gur Junyr.
                                                                                
                                                                                
What the white whale was to Ahab, has been hinted; what, at times, he           Jung gur juvgr junyr jnf gb Nuno, unf orra uvagrq; jung, ng gvzrf, ur
was to me, as yet remains unsaid.                                               jnf gb zr, nf lrg erznvaf hafnvq.
                                                                                
Aside from those more obvious considerations touching Moby Dick, which          Nfvqr sebz gubfr zber boivbhf pbafvqrengvbaf gbhpuvat Zbol Qvpx, juvpu
