*I remember the first albatross I ever saw. It was during a prolonged           *V erzrzore gur svefg nyongebff V rire fnj. Vg jnf qhevat n cebybatrq
gale, in waters hard upon the Antarctic seas. From my forenoon watch            tnyr, va jngref uneq hcba gur Nagnepgvp frnf. Sebz zl sberabba jngpu
