with a hooked, Roman bill sublime. At intervals, it arched forth                jvgu n ubbxrq, Ebzna ovyy fhoyvzr. Ng vagreinyf, vg nepurq sbegu
its vast archangel wings, as if to embrace some holy ark. Wondrous              vgf infg nepunatry jvatf, nf vs gb rzoenpr fbzr ubyl nex. Jbaqebhf
flutterings and throbbings shook it. Though bodily unharmed, it uttered         syhggrevatf naq gueboovatf fubbx vg. Gubhtu obqvyl haunezrq, vg hggrerq
cries, as some king's ghost in supernatural distress. Through its               pevrf, nf fbzr xvat'f tubfg va fhcreangheny qvfgerff. Guebhtu vgf
