conjoined, fled horror-stricken from the unbidden and unfathered birth.         pbawbvarq, syrq ubeebe-fgevpxra sebz gur haovqqra naq hasngurerq ovegu.
Therefore, the tormented spirit that glared out of bodily eyes, when            Gurersber, gur gbezragrq fcvevg gung tynerq bhg bs obqvyl rlrf, jura
what seemed Ahab rushed from his room, was for the time but a vacated           jung frrzrq Nuno ehfurq sebz uvf ebbz, jnf sbe gur gvzr ohg n inpngrq
thing, a formless somnambulistic being, a ray of living light, to be            guvat, n sbezyrff fbzanzohyvfgvp orvat, n enl bs yvivat yvtug, gb or
sure, but without an object to colour, and therefore a blankness in             fher, ohg jvgubhg na bowrpg gb pbybhe, naq gurersber n oynaxarff va
itself. God help thee, old man, thy thoughts have created a creature            vgfrys. Tbq uryc gurr, byq zna, gul gubhtugf unir perngrq n perngher
in thee; and he whose intense thinking thus makes him a Prometheus; a           va gurr; naq ur jubfr vagrafr guvaxvat guhf znxrf uvz n Cebzrgurhf; n
vulture feeds upon that heart for ever; that vulture the very creature          ihygher srrqf hcba gung urneg sbe rire; gung ihygher gur irel perngher
he creates.                                                                     ur perngrf.
                                                                                
                                                                                
                                                                                
