itself.                                                                         vgfrys.
                                                                                
First: I have personally known three instances where a whale, after             Svefg: V unir crefbanyyl xabja guerr vafgnaprf jurer n junyr, nsgre
receiving a harpoon, has effected a complete escape; and, after an              erprvivat n unecbba, unf rssrpgrq n pbzcyrgr rfpncr; naq, nsgre na
