years. A fact thus set down in substantial history cannot easily be             lrnef. N snpg guhf frg qbja va fhofgnagvny uvfgbel pnaabg rnfvyl or
gainsaid. Nor is there any reason it should be. Of what precise species         tnvafnvq. Abe vf gurer nal ernfba vg fubhyq or. Bs jung cerpvfr fcrpvrf
this sea-monster was, is not mentioned. But as he destroyed ships, as           guvf frn-zbafgre jnf, vf abg zragvbarq. Ohg nf ur qrfgeblrq fuvcf, nf
well as for other reasons, he must have been a whale; and I am strongly         jryy nf sbe bgure ernfbaf, ur zhfg unir orra n junyr; naq V nz fgebatyl
inclined to think a sperm whale. And I will tell you why. For a long            vapyvarq gb guvax n fcrez junyr. Naq V jvyy gryy lbh jul. Sbe n ybat
time I fancied that the sperm whale had been always unknown in the              gvzr V snapvrq gung gur fcrez junyr unq orra nyjnlf haxabja va gur
Mediterranean and the deep waters connecting with it. Even now I am             Zrqvgreenarna naq gur qrrc jngref pbaarpgvat jvgu vg. Rira abj V nz
certain that those seas are not, and perhaps never can be, in the               pregnva gung gubfr frnf ner abg, naq creuncf arire pna or, va gur
present constitution of things, a place for his habitual gregarious             cerfrag pbafgvghgvba bs guvatf, n cynpr sbe uvf unovghny tertnevbhf
resort. But further investigations have recently proved to me, that in          erfbeg. Ohg shegure vairfgvtngvbaf unir erpragyl cebirq gb zr, gung va
modern times there have been isolated instances of the presence of the          zbqrea gvzrf gurer unir orra vfbyngrq vafgnaprf bs gur cerfrapr bs gur
sperm whale in the Mediterranean. I am told, on good authority, that            fcrez junyr va gur Zrqvgreenarna. V nz gbyq, ba tbbq nhgubevgl, gung
on the Barbary coast, a Commodore Davis of the British navy found               ba gur Oneonel pbnfg, n Pbzzbqber Qnivf bs gur Oevgvfu anil sbhaq
the skeleton of a sperm whale. Now, as a vessel of war readily passes           gur fxryrgba bs n fcrez junyr. Abj, nf n irffry bs jne ernqvyl cnffrf
through the Dardanelles, hence a sperm whale could, by the same route,          guebhtu gur Qneqnaryyrf, urapr n fcrez junyr pbhyq, ol gur fnzr ebhgr,
pass out of the Mediterranean into the Propontis.                               cnff bhg bs gur Zrqvgreenarna vagb gur Cebcbagvf.
                                                                                
In the Propontis, as far as I can learn, none of that peculiar substance        Va gur Cebcbagvf, nf sne nf V pna yrnea, abar bs gung crphyvne fhofgnapr
