CHAPTER 51. The Spirit-Spout.                                                   PUNCGRE 51. Gur Fcvevg-Fcbhg.
                                                                                
                                                                                
Days, weeks passed, and under easy sail, the ivory Pequod had slowly            Qnlf, jrrxf cnffrq, naq haqre rnfl fnvy, gur vibel Crdhbq unq fybjyl
