southerly from St. Helena.                                                      fbhgureyl sebz Fg. Uryran.
                                                                                
It was while gliding through these latter waters that one serene and            Vg jnf juvyr tyvqvat guebhtu gurfr ynggre jngref gung bar frerar naq
