far in advance of the white bubbles at the bow. Lit up by the moon, it          sne va nqinapr bs gur juvgr ohooyrf ng gur obj. Yvg hc ol gur zbba, vg
looked celestial; seemed some plumed and glittering god uprising from           ybbxrq pryrfgvny; frrzrq fbzr cyhzrq naq tyvggrevat tbq hcevfvat sebz
the sea. Fedallah first descried this jet. For of these moonlight               gur frn. Srqnyynu svefg qrfpevrq guvf wrg. Sbe bs gurfr zbbayvtug
