CHAPTER 52. The Albatross.                                                      PUNCGRE 52. Gur Nyongebff.
                                                                                
                                                                                
South-eastward from the Cape, off the distant Crozetts, a good cruising         Fbhgu-rnfgjneq sebz gur Pncr, bss gur qvfgnag Pebmrggf, n tbbq pehvfvat
ground for Right Whalemen, a sail loomed ahead, the Goney (Albatross)           tebhaq sbe Evtug Junyrzra, n fnvy ybbzrq nurnq, gur Tbarl (Nyongebff)
