skulls?"--the same way that whalers hail--"How many barrels?" And that          fxhyyf?"--gur fnzr jnl gung junyref unvy--"Ubj znal oneeryf?" Naq gung
question once answered, pirates straightway steer apart, for they are           dhrfgvba bapr nafjrerq, cvengrf fgenvtugjnl fgrre ncneg, sbe gurl ner
infernal villains on both sides, and don't like to see overmuch of each         vasreany ivyynvaf ba obgu fvqrf, naq qba'g yvxr gb frr birezhpu bs rnpu
