hard to answer. Because, in the case of pirates, say, I should like to          uneq gb nafjre. Orpnhfr, va gur pnfr bs cvengrf, fnl, V fubhyq yvxr gb
know whether that profession of theirs has any peculiar glory about             xabj jurgure gung cebsrffvba bs gurvef unf nal crphyvne tybel nobhg
