CHAPTER 54. The Town-Ho's Story.                                                PUNCGRE 54. Gur Gbja-Ub'f Fgbel.
                                                                                
                                                                                
(AS TOLD AT THE GOLDEN INN)                                                     (NF GBYQ NG GUR TBYQRA VAA)
                                                                                
                                                                                
The Cape of Good Hope, and all the watery region round about there, is          Gur Pncr bs Tbbq Ubcr, naq nyy gur jngrel ertvba ebhaq nobhg gurer, vf
much like some noted four corners of a great highway, where you meet            zhpu yvxr fbzr abgrq sbhe pbearef bs n terng uvtujnl, jurer lbh zrrg
