It was not very long after speaking the Goney that another                      Vg jnf abg irel ybat nsgre fcrnxvat gur Tbarl gung nabgure
homeward-bound whaleman, the Town-Ho,* was encountered. She was manned          ubzrjneq-obhaq junyrzna, gur Gbja-Ub,* jnf rapbhagrerq. Fur jnf znaarq
almost wholly by Polynesians. In the short gam that ensued she gave             nyzbfg jubyyl ol Cbylarfvnaf. Va gur fubeg tnz gung rafhrq fur tnir
