which at times are said to overtake some men. This latter circumstance,         juvpu ng gvzrf ner fnvq gb biregnxr fbzr zra. Guvf ynggre pvephzfgnapr,
with its own particular accompaniments, forming what may be called the          jvgu vgf bja cnegvphyne nppbzcnavzragf, sbezvat jung znl or pnyyrq gur
secret part of the tragedy about to be narrated, never reached the ears         frperg cneg bs gur gentrql nobhg gb or aneengrq, arire ernpurq gur rnef
of Captain Ahab or his mates. For that secret part of the story was             bs Pncgnva Nuno be uvf zngrf. Sbe gung frperg cneg bs gur fgbel jnf
unknown to the captain of the Town-Ho himself. It was the private               haxabja gb gur pncgnva bs gur Gbja-Ub uvzfrys. Vg jnf gur cevingr
property of three confederate white seamen of that ship, one of whom, it        cebcregl bs guerr pbasrqrengr juvgr frnzra bs gung fuvc, bar bs jubz, vg
seems, communicated it to Tashtego with Romish injunctions of secrecy,          frrzf, pbzzhavpngrq vg gb Gnfugrtb jvgu Ebzvfu vawhapgvbaf bs frperpl,
but the following night Tashtego rambled in his sleep, and revealed             ohg gur sbyybjvat avtug Gnfugrtb enzoyrq va uvf fyrrc, naq erirnyrq
