ship, the whole of this strange affair I now proceed to put on lasting          fuvc, gur jubyr bs guvf fgenatr nssnve V abj cebprrq gb chg ba ynfgvat
record.                                                                         erpbeq.
                                                                                
                                                                                
*The ancient whale-cry upon first sighting a whale from the mast-head,          *Gur napvrag junyr-pel hcba svefg fvtugvat n junyr sebz gur znfg-urnq,
