There are three whales and three boats; and one of the boats (presumed          Gurer ner guerr junyrf naq guerr obngf; naq bar bs gur obngf (cerfhzrq
to contain the missing leg in all its original integrity) is being              gb pbagnva gur zvffvat yrt va nyy vgf bevtvany vagrtevgl) vf orvat
crunched by the jaws of the foremost whale. Any time these ten years,           pehapurq ol gur wnjf bs gur sberzbfg junyr. Nal gvzr gurfr gra lrnef,
