will find in the western clearings. But, though for ever mounted on             jvyy svaq va gur jrfgrea pyrnevatf. Ohg, gubhtu sbe rire zbhagrq ba
that stump, never a stump-speech does the poor whaleman make; but, with         gung fghzc, arire n fghzc-fcrrpu qbrf gur cbbe junyrzna znxr; ohg, jvgu
downcast eyes, stands ruefully contemplating his own amputation.                qbjapnfg rlrf, fgnaqf ehrshyyl pbagrzcyngvat uvf bja nzchgngvba.
                                                                                
Throughout the Pacific, and also in Nantucket, and New Bedford, and             Guebhtubhg gur Cnpvsvp, naq nyfb va Anaghpxrg, naq Arj Orqsbeq, naq
