little further aft, and is then attached to the short-warp--the rope            yvggyr shegure nsg, naq vf gura nggnpurq gb gur fubeg-jnec--gur ebcr
which is immediately connected with the harpoon; but previous to that           juvpu vf vzzrqvngryl pbaarpgrq jvgu gur unecbba; ohg cerivbhf gb gung
connexion, the short-warp goes through sundry mystifications too tedious        pbaarkvba, gur fubeg-jnec tbrf guebhtu fhaqel zlfgvsvpngvbaf gbb grqvbhf
to detail.                                                                      gb qrgnvy.
                                                                                
Thus the whale-line folds the whole boat in its complicated coils,              Guhf gur junyr-yvar sbyqf gur jubyr obng va vgf pbzcyvpngrq pbvyf,
twisting and writhing around it in almost every direction. All the              gjvfgvat naq jevguvat nebhaq vg va nyzbfg rirel qverpgvba. Nyy gur
oarsmen are involved in its perilous contortions; so that to the timid          bnefzra ner vaibyirq va vgf crevybhf pbagbegvbaf; fb gung gb gur gvzvq
eye of the landsman, they seem as Indian jugglers, with the deadliest           rlr bs gur ynaqfzna, gurl frrz nf Vaqvna whttyref, jvgu gur qrnqyvrfg
snakes sportively festooning their limbs. Nor can any son of mortal             fanxrf fcbegviryl srfgbbavat gurve yvzof. Abe pna nal fba bs zbegny
woman, for the first time, seat himself amid those hempen intricacies,          jbzna, sbe gur svefg gvzr, frng uvzfrys nzvq gubfr urzcra vagevpnpvrf,
and while straining his utmost at the oar, bethink him that at any              naq juvyr fgenvavat uvf hgzbfg ng gur bne, orguvax uvz gung ng nal
