contortions be put in play like ringed lightnings; he cannot be thus            pbagbegvbaf or chg va cynl yvxr evatrq yvtugavatf; ur pnaabg or guhf
circumstanced without a shudder that makes the very marrow in his bones         pvephzfgnaprq jvgubhg n fuhqqre gung znxrf gur irel zneebj va uvf obarf
to quiver in him like a shaken jelly. Yet habit--strange thing! what            gb dhvire va uvz yvxr n funxra wryyl. Lrg unovg--fgenatr guvat! jung
cannot habit accomplish?--Gayer sallies, more merry mirth, better jokes,        pnaabg unovg nppbzcyvfu?--Tnlre fnyyvrf, zber zreel zvegu, orggre wbxrf,
and brighter repartees, you never heard over your mahogany, than you            naq oevtugre ercnegrrf, lbh arire urneq bire lbhe znubtnal, guna lbh
will hear over the half-inch white cedar of the whale-boat, when thus           jvyy urne bire gur unys-vapu juvgr prqne bs gur junyr-obng, jura guhf
