any other aspect of this dangerous affair. But why say more? All men            nal bgure nfcrpg bs guvf qnatrebhf nssnve. Ohg jul fnl zber? Nyy zra
live enveloped in whale-lines. All are born with halters round their            yvir rairybcrq va junyr-yvarf. Nyy ner obea jvgu unygref ebhaq gurve
necks; but it is only when caught in the swift, sudden turn of death,           arpxf; ohg vg vf bayl jura pnhtug va gur fjvsg, fhqqra ghea bs qrngu,
that mortals realize the silent, subtle, ever-present perils of life.           gung zbegnyf ernyvmr gur fvyrag, fhogyr, rire-cerfrag crevyf bs yvsr.
And if you be a philosopher, though seated in the whale-boat, you would         Naq vs lbh or n cuvybfbcure, gubhtu frngrq va gur junyr-obng, lbh jbhyq
