Stubb's whale had been killed some distance from the ship. It was               Fghoo'f junyr unq orra xvyyrq fbzr qvfgnapr sebz gur fuvc. Vg jnf
a calm; so, forming a tandem of three boats, we commenced the slow              n pnyz; fb, sbezvat n gnaqrz bs guerr obngf, jr pbzzraprq gur fybj
