have such an eatable look that the most self-denying stranger can hardly        unir fhpu na rngnoyr ybbx gung gur zbfg frys-qralvat fgenatre pna uneqyl
keep his hands off.                                                             xrrc uvf unaqf bss.
                                                                                
But what further depreciates the whale as a civilized dish, is his              Ohg jung shegure qrcerpvngrf gur junyr nf n pvivyvmrq qvfu, vf uvf
exceeding richness. He is the great prize ox of the sea, too fat to be          rkprrqvat evpuarff. Ur vf gur terng cevmr bk bs gur frn, gbb sng gb or
delicately good. Look at his hump, which would be as fine eating as             qryvpngryl tbbq. Ybbx ng uvf uhzc, juvpu jbhyq or nf svar rngvat nf
the buffalo's (which is esteemed a rare dish), were it not such a solid         gur ohssnyb'f (juvpu vf rfgrrzrq n ener qvfu), jrer vg abg fhpu n fbyvq
pyramid of fat. But the spermaceti itself, how bland and creamy that            clenzvq bs sng. Ohg gur fcreznprgv vgfrys, ubj oynaq naq pernzl gung
is; like the transparent, half-jellied, white meat of a cocoanut in the         vf; yvxr gur genafcnerag, unys-wryyvrq, juvgr zrng bs n pbpbnahg va gur
third month of its growth, yet far too rich to supply a substitute for          guveq zbagu bs vgf tebjgu, lrg sne gbb evpu gb fhccyl n fhofgvghgr sbe
butter. Nevertheless, many whalemen have a method of absorbing it into          ohggre. Arireguryrff, znal junyrzra unir n zrgubq bs nofbeovat vg vagb
some other substance, and then partaking of it. In the long try                 fbzr bgure fhofgnapr, naq gura cnegnxvat bs vg. Va gur ybat gel
watches of the night it is a common thing for the seamen to dip their           jngpurf bs gur avtug vg vf n pbzzba guvat sbe gur frnzra gb qvc gurve
ship-biscuit into the huge oil-pots and let them fry there awhile. Many         fuvc-ovfphvg vagb gur uhtr bvy-cbgf naq yrg gurz sel gurer njuvyr. Znal
a good supper have I thus made.                                                 n tbbq fhccre unir V guhf znqr.
                                                                                
In the case of a small Sperm Whale the brains are accounted a fine dish.        Va gur pnfr bs n fznyy Fcrez Junyr gur oenvaf ner nppbhagrq n svar qvfu.
The casket of the skull is broken into with an axe, and the two plump,          Gur pnfxrg bs gur fxhyy vf oebxra vagb jvgu na nkr, naq gur gjb cyhzc,
whitish lobes being withdrawn (precisely resembling two large puddings),        juvgvfu yborf orvat jvguqenja (cerpvfryl erfrzoyvat gjb ynetr chqqvatf),
they are then mixed with flour, and cooked into a most delectable mess,         gurl ner gura zvkrq jvgu sybhe, naq pbbxrq vagb n zbfg qryrpgnoyr zrff,
in flavor somewhat resembling calves' head, which is quite a dish among         va synibe fbzrjung erfrzoyvat pnyirf' urnq, juvpu vf dhvgr n qvfu nzbat
some epicures; and every one knows that some young bucks among the              fbzr rcvpherf; naq rirel bar xabjf gung fbzr lbhat ohpxf nzbat gur
epicures, by continually dining upon calves' brains, by and by get to           rcvpherf, ol pbagvahnyyl qvavat hcba pnyirf' oenvaf, ol naq ol trg gb
have a little brains of their own, so as to be able to tell a                   unir n yvggyr oenvaf bs gurve bja, fb nf gb or noyr gb gryy n
calf's head from their own heads; which, indeed, requires uncommon              pnys'f urnq sebz gurve bja urnqf; juvpu, vaqrrq, erdhverf hapbzzba
discrimination. And that is the reason why a young buck with an                 qvfpevzvangvba. Naq gung vf gur ernfba jul n lbhat ohpx jvgu na
intelligent looking calf's head before him, is somehow one of the               vagryyvtrag ybbxvat pnys'f urnq orsber uvz, vf fbzrubj bar bs gur
saddest sights you can see. The head looks a sort of reproachfully at           fnqqrfg fvtugf lbh pna frr. Gur urnq ybbxf n fbeg bs ercebnpushyyl ng
him, with an "Et tu Brute!" expression.                                         uvz, jvgu na "Rg gh Oehgr!" rkcerffvba.
                                                                                
It is not, perhaps, entirely because the whale is so excessively                Vg vf abg, creuncf, ragveryl orpnhfr gur junyr vf fb rkprffviryl
