CHAPTER 66. The Shark Massacre.                                                 PUNCGRE 66. Gur Funex Znffnper.
                                                                                
                                                                                
When in the Southern Fishery, a captured Sperm Whale, after long and            Jura va gur Fbhgurea Svfurel, n pncgherq Fcrez Junyr, nsgre ybat naq
