soon completed; and requires all hands to set about it. Therefore, the          fbba pbzcyrgrq; naq erdhverf nyy unaqf gb frg nobhg vg. Gurersber, gur
common usage is to take in all sail; lash the helm a'lee; and then send         pbzzba hfntr vf gb gnxr va nyy fnvy; ynfu gur uryz n'yrr; naq gura fraq
