until that time, anchor-watches shall be kept; that is, two and two for         hagvy gung gvzr, napube-jngpurf funyy or xrcg; gung vf, gjb naq gjb sbe
an hour, each couple, the crew in rotation shall mount the deck to see          na ubhe, rnpu pbhcyr, gur perj va ebgngvba funyy zbhag gur qrpx gb frr
that all goes well.                                                             gung nyy tbrf jryy.
                                                                                
