afloat, and learned naturalists ashore. My original opinion remains             nsybng, naq yrnearq anghenyvfgf nfuber. Zl bevtvany bcvavba erznvaf
unchanged; but it is only an opinion.                                           hapunatrq; ohg vg vf bayl na bcvavba.
                                                                                
The question is, what and where is the skin of the whale? Already you           Gur dhrfgvba vf, jung naq jurer vf gur fxva bs gur junyr? Nyernql lbh
