was inserted into the original hole there cut by the spades of the              jnf vafregrq vagb gur bevtvany ubyr gurer phg ol gur fcnqrf bs gur
mates. But how did so clumsy and weighty a mass as that same hook               zngrf. Ohg ubj qvq fb pyhzfl naq jrvtugl n znff nf gung fnzr ubbx
get fixed in that hole? It was inserted there by my particular friend           trg svkrq va gung ubyr? Vg jnf vafregrq gurer ol zl cnegvphyne sevraq
Queequeg, whose duty it was, as harpooneer, to descend upon the                 Dhrrdhrt, jubfr qhgl vg jnf, nf unecbbarre, gb qrfpraq hcba gur
