In the first place, you are struck by the general contrast between these        Va gur svefg cynpr, lbh ner fgehpx ol gur trareny pbagenfg orgjrra gurfr
heads. Both are massive enough in all conscience; but there is a certain        urnqf. Obgu ner znffvir rabhtu va nyy pbafpvrapr; ohg gurer vf n pregnva
mathematical symmetry in the Sperm Whale's which the Right Whale's sadly        zngurzngvpny flzzrgel va gur Fcrez Junyr'f juvpu gur Evtug Junyr'f fnqyl
lacks. There is more character in the Sperm Whale's head. As you behold         ynpxf. Gurer vf zber punenpgre va gur Fcrez Junyr'f urnq. Nf lbh orubyq
