Heidelburgh Tun of the Sperm Whale. And as that famous great tierce is          Urvqryohetu Gha bs gur Fcrez Junyr. Naq nf gung snzbhf terng gvrepr vf
mystically carved in front, so the whale's vast plaited forehead forms          zlfgvpnyyl pneirq va sebag, fb gur junyr'f infg cynvgrq sberurnq sbezf
