But if from the comparative dimensions of the whale's proper brain, you         Ohg vs sebz gur pbzcnengvir qvzrafvbaf bs gur junyr'f cebcre oenva, lbh
deem it incapable of being adequately charted, then I have another idea         qrrz vg vapncnoyr bs orvat nqrdhngryl punegrq, gura V unir nabgure vqrn
for you. If you attentively regard almost any quadruped's spine,                sbe lbh. Vs lbh nggragviryl ertneq nyzbfg nal dhnqehcrq'f fcvar,
