necklace of dwarfed skulls, all bearing rudimental resemblance to the           arpxynpr bs qjnesrq fxhyyf, nyy ornevat ehqvzragny erfrzoynapr gb gur
skull proper. It is a German conceit, that the vertebrae are absolutely         fxhyy cebcre. Vg vf n Trezna pbaprvg, gung gur iregroenr ner nofbyhgryl
undeveloped skulls. But the curious external resemblance, I take it             haqrirybcrq fxhyyf. Ohg gur phevbhf rkgreany erfrzoynapr, V gnxr vg
