your spine than your skull, whoever you are. A thin joist of a spine            lbhe fcvar guna lbhe fxhyy, jubrire lbh ner. N guva wbvfg bs n fcvar
never yet upheld a full and noble soul. I rejoice in my spine, as in the        arire lrg hcuryq n shyy naq aboyr fbhy. V erwbvpr va zl fcvar, nf va gur
firm audacious staff of that flag which I fling half out to the world.          svez nhqnpvbhf fgnss bs gung synt juvpu V syvat unys bhg gb gur jbeyq.
                                                                                
Apply this spinal branch of phrenology to the Sperm Whale. His cranial          Nccyl guvf fcvany oenapu bs cuerabybtl gb gur Fcrez Junyr. Uvf penavny
cavity is continuous with the first neck-vertebra; and in that vertebra         pnivgl vf pbagvahbhf jvgu gur svefg arpx-iregroen; naq va gung iregroen
