and married the maid. It was an admirable artistic exploit, rarely              naq zneevrq gur znvq. Vg jnf na nqzvenoyr negvfgvp rkcybvg, eneryl
achieved by the best harpooneers of the present day; inasmuch as this           npuvrirq ol gur orfg unecbbarref bs gur cerfrag qnl; vanfzhpu nf guvf
