of those times, when the true form of the whale was unknown to artists;         bs gubfr gvzrf, jura gur gehr sbez bs gur junyr jnf haxabja gb negvfgf;
and considering that as in Perseus' case, St. George's whale might have         naq pbafvqrevat gung nf va Crefrhf' pnfr, Fg. Trbetr'f junyr zvtug unir
crawled up out of the sea on the beach; and considering that the animal         penjyrq hc bhg bs gur frn ba gur ornpu; naq pbafvqrevat gung gur navzny
ridden by St. George might have been only a large seal, or sea-horse;           evqqra ol Fg. Trbetr zvtug unir orra bayl n ynetr frny, be frn-ubefr;
bearing all this in mind, it will not appear altogether incompatible            ornevat nyy guvf va zvaq, vg jvyy abg nccrne nygbtrgure vapbzcngvoyr
with the sacred legend and the ancientest draughts of the scene, to             jvgu gur fnperq yrtraq naq gur napvragrfg qenhtugf bs gur fprar, gb
hold this so-called dragon no other than the great Leviathan himself. In        ubyq guvf fb-pnyyrq qentba ab bgure guna gur terng Yrivnguna uvzfrys. Va
fact, placed before the strict and piercing truth, this whole story will        snpg, cynprq orsber gur fgevpg naq cvrepvat gehgu, guvf jubyr fgbel jvyy
fare like that fish, flesh, and fowl idol of the Philistines, Dagon by          sner yvxr gung svfu, syrfu, naq sbjy vqby bs gur Cuvyvfgvarf, Qntba ol
name; who being planted before the ark of Israel, his horse's head and          anzr; jub orvat cynagrq orsber gur nex bs Vfenry, uvf ubefr'f urnq naq
both the palms of his hands fell off from him, and only the stump or            obgu gur cnyzf bs uvf unaqf sryy bss sebz uvz, naq bayl gur fghzc be
fishy part of him remained. Thus, then, one of our own noble stamp, even        svful cneg bs uvz erznvarq. Guhf, gura, bar bs bhe bja aboyr fgnzc, rira
a whaleman, is the tutelary guardian of England; and by good rights, we         n junyrzna, vf gur ghgrynel thneqvna bs Ratynaq; naq ol tbbq evtugf, jr
harpooneers of Nantucket should be enrolled in the most noble order             unecbbarref bs Anaghpxrg fubhyq or raebyyrq va gur zbfg aboyr beqre
of St. George. And therefore, let not the knights of that honourable            bs Fg. Trbetr. Naq gurersber, yrg abg gur xavtugf bs gung ubabhenoyr
company (none of whom, I venture to say, have ever had to do with a             pbzcnal (abar bs jubz, V iragher gb fnl, unir rire unq gb qb jvgu n
whale like their great patron), let them never eye a Nantucketer with           junyr yvxr gurve terng cngeba), yrg gurz arire rlr n Anaghpxrgre jvgu
disdain, since even in our woollen frocks and tarred trowsers we are            qvfqnva, fvapr rira va bhe jbbyyra sebpxf naq gneerq gebjfref jr ner
much better entitled to St. George's decoration than they.                      zhpu orggre ragvgyrq gb Fg. Trbetr'f qrpbengvba guna gurl.
                                                                                
Whether to admit Hercules among us or not, concerning this I long               Jurgure gb nqzvg Urephyrf nzbat hf be abg, pbapreavat guvf V ybat
remained dubious: for though according to the Greek mythologies, that           erznvarq qhovbhf: sbe gubhtu nppbeqvat gb gur Terrx zlgubybtvrf, gung
