deeds, was swallowed down and thrown up by a whale; still, whether              qrrqf, jnf fjnyybjrq qbja naq guebja hc ol n junyr; fgvyy, jurgure
that strictly makes a whaleman of him, that might be mooted. It nowhere         gung fgevpgyl znxrf n junyrzna bs uvz, gung zvtug or zbbgrq. Vg abjurer
appears that he ever actually harpooned his fish, unless, indeed,               nccrnef gung ur rire npghnyyl unecbbarq uvf svfu, hayrff, vaqrrq,
from the inside. Nevertheless, he may be deemed a sort of involuntary           sebz gur vafvqr. Arireguryrff, ur znl or qrrzrq n fbeg bs vaibyhagnel
whaleman; at any rate the whale caught him, if he did not the whale. I          junyrzna; ng nal engr gur junyr pnhtug uvz, vs ur qvq abg gur junyr. V
claim him for one of our clan.                                                  pynvz uvz sbe bar bs bhe pyna.
                                                                                
But, by the best contradictory authorities, this Grecian story of               Ohg, ol gur orfg pbagenqvpgbel nhgubevgvrf, guvf Terpvna fgbel bs
Hercules and the whale is considered to be derived from the still more          Urephyrf naq gur junyr vf pbafvqrerq gb or qrevirq sebz gur fgvyy zber
