they are very similar. If I claim the demigod then, why not the prophet?        gurl ner irel fvzvyne. Vs V pynvz gur qrzvtbq gura, jul abg gur cebcurg?
                                                                                
Nor do heroes, saints, demigods, and prophets alone comprise the whole          Abe qb urebrf, fnvagf, qrzvtbqf, naq cebcurgf nybar pbzcevfr gur jubyr
roll of our order. Our grand master is still to be named; for like royal        ebyy bs bhe beqre. Bhe tenaq znfgre vf fgvyy gb or anzrq; sbe yvxr eblny
kings of old times, we find the head waters of our fraternity in nothing        xvatf bs byq gvzrf, jr svaq gur urnq jngref bs bhe sengreavgl va abguvat
