as a man who rides a horse is called a horseman?                                nf n zna jub evqrf n ubefr vf pnyyrq n ubefrzna?
                                                                                
Perseus, St. George, Hercules, Jonah, and Vishnoo! there's a member-roll        Crefrhf, Fg. Trbetr, Urephyrf, Wbanu, naq Ivfuabb! gurer'f n zrzore-ebyy
for you! What club but the whaleman's can head off like that?                   sbe lbh! Jung pyho ohg gur junyrzna'f pna urnq bss yvxr gung?
                                                                                
                                                                                
                                                                                
CHAPTER 83. Jonah Historically Regarded.                                        PUNCGRE 83. Wbanu Uvfgbevpnyyl Ertneqrq.
                                                                                
                                                                                
Reference was made to the historical story of Jonah and the whale in the        Ersrerapr jnf znqr gb gur uvfgbevpny fgbel bs Wbanu naq gur junyr va gur
preceding chapter. Now some Nantucketers rather distrust this historical        cerprqvat puncgre. Abj fbzr Anaghpxrgref engure qvfgehfg guvf uvfgbevpny
