dolphin; and yet their doubting those traditions did not make those             qbycuva; naq lrg gurve qbhogvat gubfr genqvgvbaf qvq abg znxr gubfr
traditions one whit the less facts, for all that.                               genqvgvbaf bar juvg gur yrff snpgf, sbe nyy gung.
                                                                                
One old Sag-Harbor whaleman's chief reason for questioning the Hebrew           Bar byq Fnt-Uneobe junyrzna'f puvrs ernfba sbe dhrfgvbavat gur Uroerj
