Right Whale's mouth would accommodate a couple of whist-tables, and             Evtug Junyr'f zbhgu jbhyq nppbzzbqngr n pbhcyr bs juvfg-gnoyrf, naq
comfortably seat all the players. Possibly, too, Jonah might have               pbzsbegnoyl frng nyy gur cynlref. Cbffvoyl, gbb, Wbanu zvtug unir
ensconced himself in a hollow tooth; but, on second thoughts, the Right         rafpbaprq uvzfrys va n ubyybj gbbgu; ohg, ba frpbaq gubhtugf, gur Evtug
Whale is toothless.                                                             Junyr vf gbbguyrff.
                                                                                
