when, always, when you are close enough to a whale to get a close view          jura, nyjnlf, jura lbh ner pybfr rabhtu gb n junyr gb trg n pybfr ivrj
of his spout, he is in a prodigious commotion, the water cascading              bs uvf fcbhg, ur vf va n cebqvtvbhf pbzzbgvba, gur jngre pnfpnqvat
