fissure, which is countersunk into the summit of the whale's head? For          svffher, juvpu vf pbhagrefhax vagb gur fhzzvg bs gur junyr'f urnq? Sbe
even when tranquilly swimming through the mid-day sea in a calm, with           rira jura genadhvyyl fjvzzvat guebhtu gur zvq-qnl frn va n pnyz, jvgu
