Nor is it at all prudent for the hunter to be over curious touching the         Abe vf vg ng nyy cehqrag sbe gur uhagre gb or bire phevbhf gbhpuvat gur
precise nature of the whale spout. It will not do for him to be peering         cerpvfr angher bs gur junyr fcbhg. Vg jvyy abg qb sbe uvz gb or crrevat
