Wherefore, among whalemen, the spout is deemed poisonous; they try to           Jurersber, nzbat junyrzra, gur fcbhg vf qrrzrq cbvfbabhf; gurl gel gb
evade it. Another thing; I have heard it said, and I do not much doubt          rinqr vg. Nabgure guvat; V unir urneq vg fnvq, naq V qb abg zhpu qbhog
it, that if the jet is fairly spouted into your eyes, it will blind you.        vg, gung vs gur wrg vf snveyl fcbhgrq vagb lbhe rlrf, vg jvyy oyvaq lbh.
The wisest thing the investigator can do then, it seems to me, is to let        Gur jvfrfg guvat gur vairfgvtngbe pna qb gura, vg frrzf gb zr, vf gb yrg
this deadly spout alone.                                                        guvf qrnqyl fcbhg nybar.
                                                                                
Still, we can hypothesize, even if we cannot prove and establish. My            Fgvyy, jr pna ulcbgurfvmr, rira vs jr pnaabg cebir naq rfgnoyvfu. Zl
