whales sometimes are. He is both ponderous and profound. And I am               junyrf fbzrgvzrf ner. Ur vf obgu cbaqrebhf naq cebsbhaq. Naq V nz
convinced that from the heads of all ponderous profound beings, such as         pbaivaprq gung sebz gur urnqf bs nyy cbaqrebhf cebsbhaq orvatf, fhpu nf
Plato, Pyrrho, the Devil, Jupiter, Dante, and so on, there always goes          Cyngb, Cleeub, gur Qrivy, Whcvgre, Qnagr, naq fb ba, gurer nyjnlf tbrf
up a certain semi-visible steam, while in the act of thinking deep              hc n pregnva frzv-ivfvoyr fgrnz, juvyr va gur npg bs guvaxvat qrrc
thoughts. While composing a little treatise on Eternity, I had the              gubhtugf. Juvyr pbzcbfvat n yvggyr gerngvfr ba Rgreavgl, V unq gur
curiosity to place a mirror before me; and ere long saw reflected there,        phevbfvgl gb cynpr n zveebe orsber zr; naq rer ybat fnj ersyrpgrq gurer,
a curious involved worming and undulation in the atmosphere over my             n phevbhf vaibyirq jbezvat naq haqhyngvba va gur ngzbfcurer bire zl
head. The invariable moisture of my hair, while plunged in deep thought,        urnq. Gur vainevnoyr zbvfgher bs zl unve, juvyr cyhatrq va qrrc gubhtug,
after six cups of hot tea in my thin shingled attic, of an August noon;         nsgre fvk phcf bs ubg grn va zl guva fuvatyrq nggvp, bs na Nhthfg abba;
this seems an additional argument for the above supposition.                    guvf frrzf na nqqvgvbany nethzrag sbe gur nobir fhccbfvgvba.
                                                                                
And how nobly it raises our conceit of the mighty, misty monster, to            Naq ubj aboyl vg envfrf bhe pbaprvg bs gur zvtugl, zvfgl zbafgre, gb
