regards them both with equal eye.                                               ertneqf gurz obgu jvgu rdhny rlr.
                                                                                
                                                                                
                                                                                
CHAPTER 86. The Tail.                                                           PUNCGRE 86. Gur Gnvy.
                                                                                
                                                                                
Other poets have warbled the praises of the soft eye of the antelope,           Bgure cbrgf unir jneoyrq gur cenvfrf bs gur fbsg rlr bs gur nagrybcr,
and the lovely plumage of the bird that never alights; less celestial, I        naq gur ybiryl cyhzntr bs gur oveq gung arire nyvtugf; yrff pryrfgvny, V
celebrate a tail.                                                               pryroengr n gnvy.
                                                                                
Reckoning the largest sized Sperm Whale's tail to begin at that point of        Erpxbavat gur ynetrfg fvmrq Fcrez Junyr'f gnvy gb ortva ng gung cbvag bs
