At the crotch or junction, these flukes slightly overlap, then sideways         Ng gur pebgpu be whapgvba, gurfr syhxrf fyvtugyl bireync, gura fvqrjnlf
recede from each other like wings, leaving a wide vacancy between. In           erprqr sebz rnpu bgure yvxr jvatf, yrnivat n jvqr inpnapl orgjrra. Va
no living thing are the lines of beauty more exquisitely defined than in        ab yvivat guvat ner gur yvarf bs ornhgl zber rkdhvfvgryl qrsvarq guna va
the crescentic borders of these flukes. At its utmost expansion in the          gur perfpragvp obeqref bs gurfr syhxrf. Ng vgf hgzbfg rkcnafvba va gur
full grown whale, the tail will considerably exceed twenty feet across.         shyy tebja junyr, gur gnvy jvyy pbafvqrenoyl rkprrq gjragl srrg npebff.
                                                                                
