fairy's arm can transcend it.                                                   snvel'f nez pna genafpraq vg.
                                                                                
Five great motions are peculiar to it. First, when used as a fin for            Svir terng zbgvbaf ner crphyvne gb vg. Svefg, jura hfrq nf n sva sbe
progression; Second, when used as a mace in battle; Third, in sweeping;         cebterffvba; Frpbaq, jura hfrq nf n znpr va onggyr; Guveq, va fjrrcvat;
