First: Being horizontal in its position, the Leviathan's tail acts in           Svefg: Orvat ubevmbagny va vgf cbfvgvba, gur Yrivnguna'f gnvy npgf va
a different manner from the tails of all other sea creatures. It never          n qvssrerag znaare sebz gur gnvyf bs nyy bgure frn perngherf. Vg arire
wriggles. In man or fish, wriggling is a sign of inferiority. To the            jevttyrf. Va zna be svfu, jevttyvat vf n fvta bs vasrevbevgl. Gb gur
whale, his tail is the sole means of propulsion. Scroll-wise coiled             junyr, uvf gnvy vf gur fbyr zrnaf bs cebchyfvba. Fpebyy-jvfr pbvyrq
