downwards shoot out of view. Excepting the sublime BREACH--somewhere            qbjajneqf fubbg bhg bs ivrj. Rkprcgvat gur fhoyvzr OERNPU--fbzrjurer
else to be described--this peaking of the whale's flukes is perhaps the         ryfr gb or qrfpevorq--guvf crnxvat bs gur junyr'f syhxrf vf creuncf gur
grandest sight to be seen in all animated nature. Out of the bottomless         tenaqrfg fvtug gb or frra va nyy navzngrq angher. Bhg bs gur obggbzyrff
profundities the gigantic tail seems spasmodically snatching at the             cebshaqvgvrf gur tvtnagvp gnvy frrzf fcnfzbqvpnyyl fangpuvat ng gur
highest heaven. So in dreams, have I seen majestic Satan thrusting forth        uvturfg urnira. Fb va qernzf, unir V frra znwrfgvp Fngna guehfgvat sbegu
his tormented colossal claw from the flame Baltic of Hell. But in               uvf gbezragrq pbybffny pynj sebz gur synzr Onygvp bs Uryy. Ohg va
gazing at such scenes, it is all in all what mood you are in; if in             tnmvat ng fhpu fprarf, vg vf nyy va nyy jung zbbq lbh ner va; vs va
the Dantean, the devils will occur to you; if in that of Isaiah, the            gur Qnagrna, gur qrivyf jvyy bpphe gb lbh; vs va gung bs Vfnvnu, gur
