signs and symbols; that the whale, indeed, by these methods                     fvtaf naq flzobyf; gung gur junyr, vaqrrq, ol gurfr zrgubqf
intelligently conversed with the world. Nor are there wanting other             vagryyvtragyl pbairefrq jvgu gur jbeyq. Abe ner gurer jnagvat bgure
