CHAPTER 87. The Grand Armada.                                                   PUNCGRE 87. Gur Tenaq Neznqn.
                                                                                
                                                                                
The long and narrow peninsula of Malacca, extending south-eastward from         Gur ybat naq aneebj cravafhyn bs Znynppn, rkgraqvat fbhgu-rnfgjneq sebz
