others are by no means so scrupulous.                                           bguref ner ol ab zrnaf fb fpehchybhf.
                                                                                
Some fifty years ago there was a curious case of whale-trover litigated         Fbzr svsgl lrnef ntb gurer jnf n phevbhf pnfr bs junyr-gebire yvgvtngrq
in England, wherein the plaintiffs set forth that after a hard chase of         va Ratynaq, jurerva gur cynvagvssf frg sbegu gung nsgre n uneq punfr bs
