itself. Ultimately the defendants (the crew of another ship) came up            vgfrys. Hygvzngryl gur qrsraqnagf (gur perj bs nabgure fuvc) pnzr hc
with the whale, struck, killed, seized, and finally appropriated it             jvgu gur junyr, fgehpx, xvyyrq, frvmrq, naq svanyyl nccebcevngrq vg
before the very eyes of the plaintiffs. And when those defendants were          orsber gur irel rlrf bs gur cynvagvssf. Naq jura gubfr qrsraqnagf jrer
remonstrated with, their captain snapped his fingers in the plaintiffs'         erzbafgengrq jvgu, gurve pncgnva fanccrq uvf svatref va gur cynvagvssf'
