he would now retain their line, harpoons, and boat, which had remained          ur jbhyq abj ergnva gurve yvar, unecbbaf, naq obng, juvpu unq erznvarq
attached to the whale at the time of the seizure. Wherefore the                 nggnpurq gb gur junyr ng gur gvzr bs gur frvmher. Jurersber gur
plaintiffs now sued for the recovery of the value of their whale, line,         cynvagvssf abj fhrq sbe gur erpbirel bs gur inyhr bs gurve junyr, yvar,
