Mr. Erskine was counsel for the defendants; Lord Ellenborough was               Ze. Refxvar jnf pbhafry sbe gur qrsraqnagf; Ybeq Ryyraobebhtu jnf
the judge. In the course of the defence, the witty Erskine went on              gur whqtr. Va gur pbhefr bs gur qrsrapr, gur jvggl Refxvar jrag ba
