abandon her he did, so that she became a loose-fish; and therefore              nonaqba ure ur qvq, fb gung fur orpnzr n ybbfr-svfu; naq gurersber
when a subsequent gentleman re-harpooned her, the lady then became that         jura n fhofrdhrag tragyrzna er-unecbbarq ure, gur ynql gura orpnzr gung
