whale! Yet so it is. By some, ambergris is supposed to be the cause, and        junyr! Lrg fb vg vf. Ol fbzr, nzoretevf vf fhccbfrq gb or gur pnhfr, naq
by others the effect, of the dyspepsia in the whale. How to cure such           ol bguref gur rssrpg, bs gur qlfcrcfvn va gur junyr. Ubj gb pher fhpu
a dyspepsia it were hard to say, unless by administering three or four          n qlfcrcfvn vg jrer uneq gb fnl, hayrff ol nqzvavfgrevat guerr be sbhe
