I should like to conclude the chapter with the above appeal, but cannot,        V fubhyq yvxr gb pbapyhqr gur puncgre jvgu gur nobir nccrny, ohg pnaabg,
owing to my anxiety to repel a charge often made against whalemen,              bjvat gb zl nakvrgl gb ercry n punetr bsgra znqr ntnvafg junyrzra,
