hint that all whales always smell bad. Now how did this odious stigma           uvag gung nyy junyrf nyjnlf fzryy onq. Abj ubj qvq guvf bqvbhf fgvtzn
originate?                                                                      bevtvangr?
                                                                                
I opine, that it is plainly traceable to the first arrival of the               V bcvar, gung vg vf cynvayl genprnoyr gb gur svefg neeviny bs gur
Greenland whaling ships in London, more than two centuries ago. Because         Terraynaq junyvat fuvcf va Ybaqba, zber guna gjb praghevrf ntb. Orpnhfr
those whalemen did not then, and do not now, try out their oil at sea as        gubfr junyrzra qvq abg gura, naq qb abg abj, gel bhg gurve bvy ng frn nf
the Southern ships have always done; but cutting up the fresh blubber in        gur Fbhgurea fuvcf unir nyjnlf qbar; ohg phggvat hc gur serfu oyhoore va
small bits, thrust it through the bung holes of large casks, and carry          fznyy ovgf, guehfg vg guebhtu gur ohat ubyrf bs ynetr pnfxf, naq pneel
it home in that manner; the shortness of the season in those Icy Seas,          vg ubzr va gung znaare; gur fubegarff bs gur frnfba va gubfr Vpl Frnf,
and the sudden and violent storms to which they are exposed, forbidding         naq gur fhqqra naq ivbyrag fgbezf gb juvpu gurl ner rkcbfrq, sbeovqqvat
any other course. The consequence is, that upon breaking into the hold,         nal bgure pbhefr. Gur pbafrdhrapr vf, gung hcba oernxvat vagb gur ubyq,
and unloading one of these whale cemeteries, in the Greenland dock, a           naq haybnqvat bar bs gurfr junyr przrgrevrf, va gur Terraynaq qbpx, n
savor is given forth somewhat similar to that arising from excavating an        fnibe vf tvira sbegu fbzrjung fvzvyne gb gung nevfvat sebz rkpningvat na
old city grave-yard, for the foundations of a Lying-in-Hospital.                byq pvgl tenir-lneq, sbe gur sbhaqngvbaf bs n Ylvat-va-Ubfcvgny.
                                                                                
I partly surmise also, that this wicked charge against whalers may be           V cnegyl fhezvfr nyfb, gung guvf jvpxrq punetr ntnvafg junyref znl or
