operation certainly gave forth no very pleasant savor. But all this is          bcrengvba pregnvayl tnir sbegu ab irel cyrnfnag fnibe. Ohg nyy guvf vf
quite different with a South Sea Sperm Whaler; which in a voyage of four        dhvgr qvssrerag jvgu n Fbhgu Frn Fcrez Junyre; juvpu va n iblntr bs sbhe
years perhaps, after completely filling her hold with oil, does not,            lrnef creuncf, nsgre pbzcyrgryl svyyvat ure ubyq jvgu bvy, qbrf abg,
perhaps, consume fifty days in the business of boiling out; and in the          creuncf, pbafhzr svsgl qnlf va gur ohfvarff bs obvyvat bhg; naq va gur
state that it is casked, the oil is nearly scentless. The truth is, that        fgngr gung vg vf pnfxrq, gur bvy vf arneyl fpragyrff. Gur gehgu vf, gung
living or dead, if but decently treated, whales as a species are by             yvivat be qrnq, vs ohg qrpragyl gerngrq, junyrf nf n fcrpvrf ner ol
no means creatures of ill odor; nor can whalemen be recognised, as the          ab zrnaf perngherf bs vyy bqbe; abe pna junyrzra or erpbtavfrq, nf gur
people of the middle ages affected to detect a Jew in the company, by           crbcyr bs gur zvqqyr ntrf nssrpgrq gb qrgrpg n Wrj va gur pbzcnal, ol
the nose. Nor indeed can the whale possibly be otherwise than fragrant,         gur abfr. Abe vaqrrq pna gur junyr cbffvoyl or bgurejvfr guna sentenag,
when, as a general thing, he enjoys such high health; taking abundance          jura, nf n trareny guvat, ur rawblf fhpu uvtu urnygu; gnxvat nohaqnapr
of exercise; always out of doors; though, it is true, seldom in the             bs rkrepvfr; nyjnlf bhg bs qbbef; gubhtu, vg vf gehr, fryqbz va gur
