Immemorial to all his order, this investiture alone will adequately             Vzzrzbevny gb nyy uvf beqre, guvf vairfgvgher nybar jvyy nqrdhngryl
protect him, while employed in the peculiar functions of his office.            cebgrpg uvz, juvyr rzcyblrq va gur crphyvne shapgvbaf bs uvf bssvpr.
                                                                                
That office consists in mincing the horse-pieces of blubber for the             Gung bssvpr pbafvfgf va zvapvat gur ubefr-cvrprf bs oyhoore sbe gur
pots; an operation which is conducted at a curious wooden horse, planted        cbgf; na bcrengvba juvpu vf pbaqhpgrq ng n phevbhf jbbqra ubefr, cynagrq
