desk. Arrayed in decent black; occupying a conspicuous pulpit; intent           qrfx. Neenlrq va qrprag oynpx; bpphclvat n pbafcvphbhf chycvg; vagrag
on bible leaves; what a candidate for an archbishopric, what a lad for a        ba ovoyr yrnirf; jung n pnaqvqngr sbe na nepuovfubcevp, jung n ynq sbe n
Pope were this mincer!*                                                         Cbcr jrer guvf zvapre!*
                                                                                
                                                                                
*Bible leaves! Bible leaves! This is the invariable cry from the mates          *Ovoyr yrnirf! Ovoyr yrnirf! Guvf vf gur vainevnoyr pel sebz gur zngrf
to the mincer. It enjoins him to be careful, and cut his work into as           gb gur zvapre. Vg rawbvaf uvz gb or pnershy, naq phg uvf jbex vagb nf
thin slices as possible, inasmuch as by so doing the business of                guva fyvprf nf cbffvoyr, vanfzhpu nf ol fb qbvat gur ohfvarff bs
