It is as if from the open field a brick-kiln were transported to her            Vg vf nf vs sebz gur bcra svryq n oevpx-xvya jrer genafcbegrq gb ure
planks.                                                                         cynaxf.
                                                                                
The try-works are planted between the foremast and mainmast, the most           Gur gel-jbexf ner cynagrq orgjrra gur sberznfg naq znvaznfg, gur zbfg
