expense, the British government was induced to send the sloop-of-war            rkcrafr, gur Oevgvfu tbireazrag jnf vaqhprq gb fraq gur fybbc-bs-jne
Rattler on a whaling voyage of discovery into the South Sea. Commanded          Enggyre ba n junyvat iblntr bs qvfpbirel vagb gur Fbhgu Frn. Pbzznaqrq
by a naval Post-Captain, the Rattler made a rattling voyage of it, and          ol n aniny Cbfg-Pncgnva, gur Enggyre znqr n enggyvat iblntr bs vg, naq
did some service; how much does not appear. But this is not all. In             qvq fbzr freivpr; ubj zhpu qbrf abg nccrne. Ohg guvf vf abg nyy. Va
