CHAPTER 105. Does the Whale's Magnitude Diminish?--Will He Perish?              PUNCGRE 105. Qbrf gur Junyr'f Zntavghqr Qvzvavfu?--Jvyy Ur Crevfu?
                                                                                
                                                                                
Inasmuch, then, as this Leviathan comes floundering down upon us from           Vanfzhpu, gura, nf guvf Yrivnguna pbzrf sybhaqrevat qbja hcba hf sebz
