Comparing the humped herds of whales with the humped herds of buffalo,          Pbzcnevat gur uhzcrq ureqf bs junyrf jvgu gur uhzcrq ureqf bs ohssnyb,
which, not forty years ago, overspread by tens of thousands the prairies        juvpu, abg sbegl lrnef ntb, birefcernq ol graf bs gubhfnaqf gur cenvevrf
