of the sea combined.                                                            bs gur frn pbzovarq.
                                                                                
Moreover: we are to consider, that from the presumed great longevity            Zberbire: jr ner gb pbafvqre, gung sebz gur cerfhzrq terng ybatrivgl
of whales, their probably attaining the age of a century and more,              bs junyrf, gurve cebonoyl nggnvavat gur ntr bs n praghel naq zber,
