Wherefore, for all these things, we account the whale immortal in his           Jurersber, sbe nyy gurfr guvatf, jr nppbhag gur junyr vzzbegny va uvf
species, however perishable in his individuality. He swam the seas              fcrpvrf, ubjrire crevfunoyr va uvf vaqvivqhnyvgl. Ur fjnz gur frnf
before the continents broke water; he once swam over the site of the            orsber gur pbagvaragf oebxr jngre; ur bapr fjnz bire gur fvgr bs gur
Tuileries, and Windsor Castle, and the Kremlin. In Noah's flood he              Ghvyrevrf, naq Jvaqfbe Pnfgyr, naq gur Xerzyva. Va Abnu'f sybbq ur
