The one grand stage where he enacted all his various parts so manifold,         Gur bar tenaq fgntr jurer ur ranpgrq nyy uvf inevbhf cnegf fb znavsbyq,
was his vice-bench; a long rude ponderous table furnished with several          jnf uvf ivpr-orapu; n ybat ehqr cbaqrebhf gnoyr sheavfurq jvgu frireny
