except when whales were alongside, this bench was securely lashed               rkprcg jura junyrf jrer nybatfvqr, guvf orapu jnf frpheryl ynfurq
athwartships against the rear of the Try-works.                                 ngujnegfuvcf ntnvafg gur erne bs gur Gel-jbexf.
                                                                                
