CHAPTER 109. Ahab and Starbuck in the Cabin.                                    PUNCGRE 109. Nuno naq Fgneohpx va gur Pnova.
                                                                                
                                                                                
According to usage they were pumping the ship next morning; and lo! no          Nppbeqvat gb hfntr gurl jrer chzcvat gur fuvc arkg zbeavat; naq yb! ab
inconsiderable oil came up with the water; the casks below must have            vapbafvqrenoyr bvy pnzr hc jvgu gur jngre; gur pnfxf orybj zhfg unir
sprung a bad leak. Much concern was shown; and Starbuck went down into          fcehat n onq yrnx. Zhpu pbaprea jnf fubja; naq Fgneohpx jrag qbja vagb
the cabin to report this unfavourable affair.*                                  gur pnova gb ercbeg guvf hasnibhenoyr nssnve.*
                                                                                
                                                                                
*In Sperm-whalemen with any considerable quantity of oil on board, it           *Va Fcrez-junyrzra jvgu nal pbafvqrenoyr dhnagvgl bs bvy ba obneq, vg
is a regular semiweekly duty to conduct a hose into the hold, and drench        vf n erthyne frzvjrrxyl qhgl gb pbaqhpg n ubfr vagb gur ubyq, naq qerapu
