CHAPTER 125. The Log and Line.                                                  PUNCGRE 125. Gur Ybt naq Yvar.
                                                                                
                                                                                
While now the fated Pequod had been so long afloat this voyage, the log         Juvyr abj gur sngrq Crdhbq unq orra fb ybat nsybng guvf iblntr, gur ybt
and line had but very seldom been in use. Owing to a confident reliance         naq yvar unq ohg irel fryqbz orra va hfr. Bjvat gb n pbasvqrag eryvnapr
