wind had warped it; all the elements had combined to rot a thing that           jvaq unq jnecrq vg; nyy gur ryrzragf unq pbzovarq gb ebg n guvat gung
hung so idly. But heedless of all this, his mood seized Ahab, as he             uhat fb vqyl. Ohg urrqyrff bs nyy guvf, uvf zbbq frvmrq Nuno, nf ur
