Here be it said, that this pertinacious pursuit of one particular whale,        Urer or vg fnvq, gung guvf cregvanpvbhf chefhvg bs bar cnegvphyne junyr,
continued through day into night, and through night into day, is a thing        pbagvahrq guebhtu qnl vagb avtug, naq guebhtu avtug vagb qnl, vf n guvat
by no means unprecedented in the South sea fishery. For such is the             ol ab zrnaf hacerprqragrq va gur Fbhgu frn svfurel. Sbe fhpu vf gur
wonderful skill, prescience of experience, and invincible confidence            jbaqreshy fxvyy, cerfpvrapr bs rkcrevrapr, naq vaivapvoyr pbasvqrapr
