that from the simple observation of a whale when last descried, they            gung sebz gur fvzcyr bofreingvba bs n junyr jura ynfg qrfpevrq, gurl
will, under certain given circumstances, pretty accurately foretell both        jvyy, haqre pregnva tvira pvephzfgnaprf, cerggl npphengryl sbergryy obgu
the direction in which he will continue to swim for a time, while out of        gur qverpgvba va juvpu ur jvyy pbagvahr gb fjvz sbe n gvzr, juvyr bhg bs
sight, as well as his probable rate of progression during that period.          fvtug, nf jryy nf uvf cebonoyr engr bs cebterffvba qhevat gung crevbq.
And, in these cases, somewhat as a pilot, when about losing sight of            Naq, va gurfr pnfrf, fbzrjung nf n cvybg, jura nobhg ybfvat fvtug bs
a coast, whose general trending he well knows, and which he desires             n pbnfg, jubfr trareny geraqvat ur jryy xabjf, naq juvpu ur qrfverf
shortly to return to again, but at some further point; like as this             fubegyl gb erghea gb ntnva, ohg ng fbzr shegure cbvag; yvxr nf guvf
pilot stands by his compass, and takes the precise bearing of the               cvybg fgnaqf ol uvf pbzcnff, naq gnxrf gur cerpvfr ornevat bs gur
cape at present visible, in order the more certainly to hit aright              pncr ng cerfrag ivfvoyr, va beqre gur zber pregnvayl gb uvg nevtug
the remote, unseen headland, eventually to be visited: so does the              gur erzbgr, hafrra urnqynaq, riraghnyyl gb or ivfvgrq: fb qbrf gur
fisherman, at his compass, with the whale; for after being chased, and          svfurezna, ng uvf pbzcnff, jvgu gur junyr; sbe nsgre orvat punfrq, naq
diligently marked, through several hours of daylight, then, when night          qvyvtragyl znexrq, guebhtu frireny ubhef bs qnlyvtug, gura, jura avtug
obscures the fish, the creature's future wake through the darkness              bofpherf gur svfu, gur perngher'f shgher jnxr guebhtu gur qnexarff
is almost as established to the sagacious mind of the hunter, as the            vf nyzbfg nf rfgnoyvfurq gb gur fntnpvbhf zvaq bs gur uhagre, nf gur
pilot's coast is to him. So that to this hunter's wondrous skill, the           cvybg'f pbnfg vf gb uvz. Fb gung gb guvf uhagre'f jbaqebhf fxvyy, gur
proverbial evanescence of a thing writ in water, a wake, is to all              cebireovny rinarfprapr bs n guvat jevg va jngre, n jnxr, vf gb nyy
